OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'When I see the boys going 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto school, it hurts'       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, "Every day I wake up with the hope of  
OL,6, going back to school. They (the        
OL,7, Taliban) keep saying they will open    
OL,8, schools. But it's been almost two years
OL,9, now. I don't believe them. It breaks my
OL,10, heart," says 17-year-old Habiba.       
OL,12,FShe blinks and bites her lip trying    
OL,13,Fhard not to tear up.                   
OL,15,FHabiba and her former classmates Mahtab
OL,16,Fand Tamana are among hundreds of       
OL,17,Fthousands of teenage girls who have    
OL,18,Fbeen barred from attending secondary   
OL,19,Fschool in most of Afghanistan by the   
OL,20,FTaliban - the only country to take such
OL,21,Faction.                                
